== 爭議 ==
任職於诺基亚CEO期間，靠攏微軟作業系統的作為被許多人認為是「木馬」，所以往後有被一些人嘲弄為trojan.win32.elop（按照習慣木馬命名原則）。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tech.feng.com/2015-06-19/Stephen-Elop-biographic-sketches-of-code-Mauritius-Win32.-Elop_616859.shtml |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-04-29 |archive-date=2016-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161006101022/http://tech.feng.com/2015-06-19/Stephen-Elop-biographic-sketches-of-code-Mauritius-Win32.-Elop_616859.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

